        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1533.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "田んぼは……無事！？　は～～、良かった～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rice paddy… Is it okay!? Haa~‚ thank goodness~~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9000000874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.666579300001,
          "startTime": 7.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4333335241
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5207028628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……？　雫ちゃんとこころちゃん！？\nどうしてここにいるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? Shizuku-chan and Kokoro!?\nWhat are you doing here!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0333336592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9865303597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、天気予報を見て、いてもたってもいられなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday‚ I saw the weather forecast‚ and I couldn’t just sit still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9865303597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5531972648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうどオフだったし\n農家さん達と、田んぼ、守り抜いた……ぶい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Luckily‚ I had the day off‚\nso I protected the rice paddy… with the farmers… V.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5531972648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9198636931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達がわざわざ来なくても、なんとかなったとは\n思いますけど……まぁ、自分達の田んぼですし？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it would've been fine even if Kokoro hadn’t come\nall the way out here‚ but… well‚ it’s our rice paddy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あのアイドル、名前貸しだけで何もしなかったー\nとか、後で週刊誌に書かれたら、たまりませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something like \"That idol just lent her name and didn’t do anything~\"\nwas written in the tabloids‚ I couldn't take it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9445587081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7570973001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと言ってるけど……こころちゃんが誰よりも\n一生懸命で……対策、凄く頑張ってて……愛を感じた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s saying this‚ but… Kokoro-chan was the most\ndedicated… She really worked hard on dealing with it… I felt her love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3237642052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そういう情報は言わなくていいんです。それに\n愛ってなんですか！　適当なこと言わないで下さいよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t need to say that kind of information. And\nwhat do you mean 'love'! Please stop saying nonsense~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.8221760991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも……！\n私の企画なのに……私、来れなくて……ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two…!\nIt's my project‚ but… I couldn't come… I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3356460652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.8305660807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。スタッフさんに……\nすみれちゃんに連絡しないでって頼んだのは、私達",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. We were the ones…\nwho asked the staff‚ not to contact Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0305663191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.6638994141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6638994141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7470698003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんには、ライブバトルに……\n専念してほしかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We wanted Sumire-chan to…\nconcentrate on the live battle…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6137367054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.9470698003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "大雨対策で忙しくて……\n連絡も返せなくて、こっちこそ、ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was busy dealing with the heavy rain…\nand couldn’t reply. I’m the one‚ who should be sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7137367054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.913736467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "全然だよ！　むしろ、謝らないで！\n田んぼを守ってくれて本当にありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry! Actually‚ don't say sorry!\nThank you so much for protecting the rice paddy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7356460652,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3964.3539348000018,
          "startTime": 96.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.4960909331
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2294108038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "わわ、すみれちゃん……急に抱き着かないで……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ whoa‚ Sumire-chan… Don’t hug me suddenly…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2294108038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 97.2294108038
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7703.922529500005,
          "startTime": 104.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7960774705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。こころの働きに感謝して下さ……ぐえ\nちょっと！　力が強過ぎますよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. Be grateful for Kokoro’s work… Gueh.\nHey! This is too strong~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2858917838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、すっごく嬉しくて！　えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. I’m just so happy! Ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2858917838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.1174986805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "この調子なら、いっぱい収穫出来ちゃうかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ we might be able to harvest a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1174986805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.1239383982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなったら、農家さんやスタッフさん以外の\n地元の人達にも、おしるこ食べてもらいたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that happens‚ I want not only farmers and staff‚\nbut the locals also eat the oshiruko.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1921229762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.1360925323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね～、かなりお世話になっちゃってますし\n後は、せっかくの企画ですから、もう一捻り……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right~. We’ve been indebted to them quite a lot‚\nand since it’s a special project‚ let’s add one more twist…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4666595459,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7132.453028599997,
          "startTime": 137.5991125745
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4666595459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十月、某日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――October‚ a certain day",
