    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "もち米も作れたのに、おしるこ缶まで……！\n夢みたい！　最高のプレゼントありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to make mochi‚ and now even an oshiruko can…!\nIt’s like a dream! Thank you for the best present!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.4702099886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "（自分の好きなもので、好きな街を応援出来て）\n（凄く嬉しいな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m so happy that I can support）\n（the city I love.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.4035412874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "（あのおしるこイベントの後、山形県のもち米）\n（アンバサダーにも選んでもらって）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After that oshiruko event‚ I was also chosen as the ambassador）\n（for Yamagata Prefecture's glutinous rice‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.3035107698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "（この撮影のお仕事もさせてもらえたし。やりたいこと）\n（やろうって言ってくれた、二人には大感謝だよ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（and I was able to do this filming job.）\n（I’m so grateful to you two for saying I should do what I want to do!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.0701509879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
