      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_03-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "（これからは遠慮しないで、お仕事でもそれ以外でも）\n（自分のやりたいことをやっていけたらいいな）",
      "translations": {
